      <title>丹麦加快为妇女强制服兵役的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/denmark-speeds-up-plans-for-mandatory-military-service-for-women</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦将从明年开始开始起草妇女进入军队，加速计划的改革，以增加其武装部队的规模，并有助于应对俄罗斯的威胁增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/denmark-speeds-up-plans-for-mandatory-military-service-for-women</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 16:43:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达利奥（Dalio</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/dalio-warns-house-gop-of-debt-peril-as-lawmakers-weigh-tax-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参加会议的议员说，布里奇沃特员工的创始人雷·达利奥（Ray Dalio）警告众议院共和党人有增加美国赤字的危险，并敦促他们控制支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/dalio-warns-house-gop-of-debt-peril-as-lawmakers-weigh-tax-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 16:15:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的哥伦比亚资金停止提起学术联盟诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-columbia-funding-halt-draws-suit-from-academic-unions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两个教育工会起诉特朗普政府从哥伦比亚大学收到4亿美元的联邦资金，称此举是为了限制校园内的学术独立和言论自由的非法企图。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-s-columbia-funding-halt-draws-suit-from-academic-unions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:57:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择在裁员期间保护社会保障的承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-pick-pledges-to-protect-social-security-amid-doge-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的提名人周二领导社会保障局（Social Security Administration）称自己为“效率人”，并说他没有考虑过将该机构私有化，这已成为埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）戏剧性的成本削减成本的主要目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-pick-pledges-to-protect-social-security-amid-doge-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:35:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>各州说，违反命令释放联邦支出的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-still-not-unfreezing-all-federal-funds-states-tell-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一群民主党领导的州再次指责唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府未能释放数亿美元的联邦灾难资金，违反了法院命令，这是白宫混乱的一月支出冻结的最新诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-still-not-unfreezing-all-federal-funds-states-tell-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 15:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国看到俄罗斯，乌克兰选择更长的战争而不是一笔不良交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/russia-ukraine-see-unsatisfactory-ceasefire-worse-than-continued-war-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国情报界的一项评估，俄罗斯和乌克兰可能会看到更大的动力延长三年冲突，而不是急于达成完整的解决方案，该评估与唐纳德·特朗普总统的承诺迅速结束了为期三年的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/russia-ukraine-see-unsatisfactory-ceasefire-worse-than-continued-war-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 14:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在记者透露也门罢工聊天后支持华尔兹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对迈克尔·沃尔兹（Michael Waltz）表示信心，因为国家安全顾问将一名记者在一个文本小组中包括在一个也门的军事罢工计划中，而美国前两位情报官员表示没有分享任何机密信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 13:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国说，俄罗斯和乌克兰同意在黑海停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰已同意在黑海停火，并制定了实施对能源基础设施罢工的禁令的机制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在绩效问题上丢下移民酒店公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/labour-scraps-2-billion-a-year-migrant-hotels-contract</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府正在与一家为寻求庇护者提供住宿的公司建立联系，理由是“物有所值”的问题，其中包括其绩效和行为缺陷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/labour-scraps-2-billion-a-year-migrant-hotels-contract</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 07:50:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其资产反弹，因为Simsek发誓要恢复稳定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/turkey-finance-czar-will-meet-investors-to-ease-pressure-on-lira</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当高级经济官员试图向外国投资者保证上周拘留伊斯坦布尔市长Ekrem Imamoglu时，土耳其的债券和股票反弹，这一举动触发了数十亿美元的外流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/turkey-finance-czar-will-meet-investors-to-ease-pressure-on-lira</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 04:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
